    "See here.• LLMs can require significant computational resources for both training and run, which may incur high costs and consume significant amounts of energy.",
    "This has consequences for nature and environment.",
    "A further issue is that few institutions have the ability to train LLMs using large-scale data, which could result in research in this field being less accessible to a wider range of people.• The fair evaluation and comparison of LLMs remains an ongoing issue, despite the availability of datasets designed for this purpose.",
    "The primary obstacle lies in gathering questions that are unlikely to be present in the training set of these LLMs, given that these models continually crawl the web for data.",
    "Additionally, it is difficult to ascertain whether ChatGPT has come across a particular question before due to the inaccessible nature of the training set."
